_______________________________________________________________________________
"Mental Beacon"
        Through the use of this power, the psionicist can temporarily
        anchor the Convergence to his current location. This will
        allow him or her to subsequently Teleport to that location.
        A psionicist may have only one beacon at a time, and may
        not create a second until the first one disappears. A beacon
        may be created to be either private or shared, and will last
        for several minutes - its duration is proportional to guild
        level.
        The cost for creating a private beacon is 100sp, and the
        cost for a shared beacon is 150sp.
 
SP Cost:  100/150       Guild Level:  14        Potential Points:  4
 
Command:  beacon, beacon here (to immediately dismiss an old beacon),
          or beacon shared [here] (to make a shared beacon)
